    public static final class NotificationChannelDescriptor.Builder
extends GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<NotificationChannelDescriptor.Builder>
implements NotificationChannelDescriptorOrBuilder
     A description of a notification channel. The descriptor includes
 the properties of the channel and the set of labels or fields that
 must be specified to configure channels of a given type.
    Protobuf type google.monitoring.v3.NotificationChannelDescriptor
